      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Organizations\" title=\"Organizations\">Organizations</a> * Darmstadt University of Technology</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:TU_Darmstadt_19th_century.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/TU_Darmstadt_19th_century.jpg/330px-TU_Darmstadt_19th_century.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"224\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e4/TU_Darmstadt_19th_century.jpg/500px-TU_Darmstadt_19th_century.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/e/e4/TU_Darmstadt_19th_century.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:TU_Darmstadt_19th_century.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>TU Darmstadt <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Darmstadt University of Technology</b> (TU Darmstadt), <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Darmstadt\">Darmstadt</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Germany\">Germany</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#People\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">People</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Engines\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Engines</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</